# Title: Potential Chrome Frame Helper DLL Sideloading
# Author: Nasreddine Bencherchali (Nextron Systems), Wietze Beukema (project and research)
# Date: 2022-08-17
# Level: medium
# Description: Detects potential DLL sideloading of "chrome_frame_helper.dll"
# MITRE Tactic: Persistence
# Tags: attack.persistence, attack.privilege-escalation, attack.execution, attack.stealth, attack.t1574.001
# Reference: https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/master/rules/windows/image_load/image_load_side_load_chrome_frame_helper.yml

ImageLoaded="*\\chrome_frame_helper.dll" NOT (ImageLoaded IN ("C:\\Program Files\\Google\\Chrome\\Application\\*", "C:\\Program Files (x86)\\Google\\Chrome\\Application\\*")) NOT ImageLoaded="*\\AppData\\local\\Google\\Chrome\\Application\\*"